text: Kevin Knopf (born 14 October 1996) is a German darts player currently playing in Professional Darts Corporation events. Nicknamed "The Button", Knopf first qualified for a PDC European Tour in 2019, when he qualified for the 2019 German Darts Championship. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:German darts players Category:Professional Darts Corporation players Category:1996 births
